# BuzzCoinAuthority

InBuzzWeTrust

BuzzCoinAuthority is the governance and mint infrastructure for BuzzCoin.

This repository defines the genesis authority layer responsible for:

- coin issuance
- identity-bound ownership registry
- execution signing authority
- treasury allocation and distribution
- ledger integrity verification
- key rotation and revocation policy
- epoch-based trust enforcement

## Authority Root
Fredrick Buzz Flowers  
Identity: figuripv6o

## Genesis State
Epoch: 00000001  
Authority State: ACTIVE

## Governance Rules
- All execution must be signed by a trusted authority
- Revoked identities are permanently denied
- Minimum epoch enforcement is global and fail-closed
- Treasury actions must be policy-valid before execution
- Deterministic policy is the default execution mode
